DATA LICENSES

This software displays data from the following public sources:

1. CalEnviroScreen 4.0
   - Source: California Office of Environmental Health Hazard Assessment (OEHHA)
   - License: Public Domain (California State Government)
   - URL: https://oehha.ca.gov/calenviroscreen

2. EPA Envirofacts Data
   - Source: U.S. Environmental Protection Agency
   - License: Public Domain (U.S. Federal Government)
   - URL: https://www.epa.gov/enviro

3. U.S. Census Bureau Data
   - Source: U.S. Census Bureau, American Community Survey
   - License: Public Domain (U.S. Federal Government)
   - URL: https://www.census.gov/programs-surveys/acs

All government data remains in the public domain and is not subject to copyright.
